{
  "stem": "25381.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they brought me in, and first they took to the police station.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they took already all the people from the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was a huge-- a huge building in the police station.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the screaming and the shouting was one and the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The seventh heaven.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were already dead before one was stepping on the other, because it was like it says, but 2,000, 3,000 people in such a room, small.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So there was a door.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they brought in-- so one policeman stays on one side of the door, and the other stays on the other side.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they bring the people and they check in their mouths if they still having gold, or maybe a ring or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they have with-- with pliers, and they pulled the tooth from the mouth with the pliers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the gold, or watches, or whatever they had-- so they put it on a side.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I walked in-- before me, what I saw with my own eyes, and I walk in and he says, oh, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He says, she's such a cute Jewish girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Why to kill her?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I looked at them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Why me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Am I the only one?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There's so many nice Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I think, why me, [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he says-- and they didn't-- they look in my mouth, I didn't-- I was young.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I didn't have any gold anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't pull me in in that room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they say, go in the other room and hide yourself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after the slaughter is going to be over, then-- then you're going to go out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't push me in in the room where the thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This, I believe in a miracle, because why me?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
